                          </svg>
                          <span class="details-box__numbering">2.</span>DELIVERY METHOD
                      </h3>

                  </div>

                  <div class="details-content details-content--row">
                      <h4 class="details-content__title details-content__title--spaced">
                          How do you want your order delivered?
